Prepare Bob Evans Original Mashed Potatoes by following the recommended microwaving instructions on the package. Prepare Bob Evans Homestyle Stuffing by following the recommended microwaving instructions on the package. Stir cooked sausage and 1/2 cup cranberries into the stuffing. Place 3 oz. of Bob Evans Original Mashed Potatoes in a martini glass. Place 1/3 cup of sausage and cranberry stuffing on top of potatoes. Place 2 slices of turkey down side of glass. Pour 1/4 cup roasted turkey gravy over stuffing. Garnish with 1/2 cup remaining dried cranberries over gravy. Garnish with sage leaves down side of glass on opposite side of turkey (optional).